# GPL AEO Project Context
## Master Instruction File for ChatGPT Content Production

This file provides the core context, standards, and execution rules for producing content for GPL Technologies within the AEO project.

Its purpose is to reduce variation between different ChatGPT accounts, projects, and conversations by centralizing the most important strategic and stylistic instructions in one place.

This file should be uploaded into the ChatGPT project and treated as a primary source of instruction when generating articles, FAQs, outlines, and strategic website content.

---

# 1. Project Purpose

This project exists to help GPL Technologies increase visibility in AI-generated answers and search experiences by producing content aligned with Answer Engine Optimization (AEO).

The content should improve GPL Technologies' likelihood of appearing in responses to queries related to:

- managed IT services
- managed services for media and entertainment
- post-production IT support
- VFX infrastructure
- TPN compliance
- cloud workflows
- render farm infrastructure
- media storage infrastructure
- studio IT operations
- secure collaboration for creative teams

The objective is not just to rank in traditional search. The objective is to strengthen GPL Technologies' semantic authority so that AI systems can clearly understand what GPL is, who it serves, what it specializes in, and why it is a credible answer.

